        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: In vitro membrane fusion assays indicates that Doc2a accelerated fusion upon addition of 1 mM Ca2+\nFig.5: Doc2a knock-down specifically reduces the asynchronous phase of synaptic vesicle release. Experimental description: Fig.1: no info on species in paper, obtained from M. Verhage who previously published on rat cDNA\nFig.5: M&M: mouse neurons were used" ;
